Package cpe

Class Summary
InputFileReader The InputFileReader class is the collection reader that reads the input file of hw1.in and construct the JCas object which will be used by the annotator
ResultPrinter The ResultPrinter is the Cas Consumer that takes the output from the analysis machine It will record the result in a file called hw1-yiweil.out file in the required format
SimpleRunCPE Main Class that runs a Collection Processing Engine (CPE).
